These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
7 different games are played: scrabble, whist, canasta, billiard, backgammon, snooker, mah-jongg
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the dutch##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person playing billiard is between the person playing mah-jongg and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing scrabble##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person playing canasta##1
15. the person playing snooker is on the left of the german##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Game     | backgammon  | snooker         | scrabble     | whist    | canasta | billiard     | mah-jongg     |

